edu.mit.jwi.item
Class Version

java.lang.Object
  edu.mit.jwi.item.Version
All Implemented Interfaces:
IVersion
public class Version
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVersion

Default, concrete implementation of the IVersion interface. This class, much like the Integer class, caches instances which are created via the createVersion(int, int, int) method.

Clients should use the createVersion(int, int, int) method to instantiate objects of this class.

Since:
1.5.0
Version:
2.1.5, Jan 22, 2008
Author:
Mark A. Finlayson
